name: Maris Brood, Fallen Jedi
Lore: 'With only a few Jedi remaining in the galaxy, each confrontation between them has far reaching consequences. Female.',
Text: 'Matching weapon is Elegant Lightsaber and, if Sai''torr Kal Fas on table, may lose 2 Force to deploy it on her from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.  While with Galen or a [Sidious] Effect, adds one battle destiny.  Immune to [Permanent Weapon] weapons and attrition < 5.',
